Title: Weekly: The Next Van Pelt
Descriptions: Survivors! Behold the relentless march of the dinosaurs, a constant threat to our very existence! We summon forth your unyielding courage once more, extending this weekly bounty to an unprecedented challenge: eliminate not merely 25, but a staggering 100 of these colossal creatures that prowl our lands! Week after week, our struggle persists, and in this crucible of survival, your unwavering dedication shines as our beacon of hope. Let our unity stand as a testament to our strength! Rally against these ancient behemoths, fortify our camp's defenses, and seize the rewards rightfully yours! The drums of war beat louder, and Arvandus Metalsmith beckons you to embark on this daring quest! Will you answer the call?
